quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,By the snorting chargers
  100,2,"by the strikers of sparks [with their hoofs]"
  100,3,by the raiders at dawn
  100,4,raising therein a trail of dust
  100,5,and cleaving therein a host
  100,6,Indeed man is ungrateful to his Lord
  100,7,"and indeed he is [himself] witness to that"
  100,8,And indeed he is an avid lover of wealth
  100,9,"Does he not know, when what is [buried] in the graves is turned over"
  100,10,"and what is [concealed] in the breasts is divulged"
  100,11,"on that day their Lord will be well informed about them [and their deeds]"